data.title: Charlie Chan at the Opera
data.meta_description: Charlie Chan at the Opera (1937) starring Warner Oland, Boris Karloff, Keye Luke and directed by H. Bruce Humberstone.
data.text: In a gripping tale of mystery, an amnesiac fugitive surfaces at the opera, entwined in a web of vengeance and deception. As Charlie Chan unravels secrets buried for 13 years, shocking revelations threaten to silence both the past and the music forever.
